summary: An Ordinance changing and establishing the curb grades on East Madison Street from a point thirty-three and seventy-five one- hundredths (33.75) feet east of the southwesterly corner of Block One (1), Werett's Addition to the City of Seattle to New Eleventh Avenue; East Spring Street from Tenth Avenue to Eleventh Avenue; Spring Place from Old Tenth Avenue to East Madison Street, and New Tenth Avenue from East Madison Street to East Union Street, all in the City of Seattle.
